<plot>Paul (aka Pablo) is a Mexican-American living with his family in California as he struggles to break his way into the world of stand-up comedy. His efforts meet with success, but his use of Mexican stereotypes to win over Anglo-Saxon audiences does not go over well with his family. Somehow, Paul must find a way to balance the two if he wants to live in peace.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?673247</url></doc>
